Prepare yourself, this is the end...!!

Your persistence is futile!! Resign yourself, Chancellor.
You cannot defeat me...!

Chancellor: Impressive swordsmanship. It seems you've
improved your skills as a knight. Even as an enemy, I must
honor your dedication to this country.

Chancellor: However, that is precisely why you were too
late...!!

Chancellor: Your knightly spirit, never losing respect for
your opponent even in battle, has become your downfall. You
should have cut me down without a second thought, rather
than being fixated on defeating me.

Chancellor: This is not a match. What are you doing taking
your time in front of the captured princess? Or is it
because it's in front of the princess? Kukuku...

Chancellor: It means I've bought enough time. Look, she's
about to wake up.

Chancellor: Now, Princess, it's time for your meal. And it's
going to be a lavish one...!

You've regained consciousness, haven't you!? Princess! It's
Reisha! I've just returned from my journey!! Come, let's
leave this place together!!
Yes! It's Knight Reisha! Your servant!!

Princess: Reisha... my... knight... ugh, ughhhhh...
ahhh...!!!
Stay strong! I will save you now!!
Stop it, stop it!! Chancellor!! You bastard!!!

Chancellor: You can feel it, can't you? The great flow of
magical power filling this place.

Chancellor: If after seeing this you still think she's the
same little girl as before, then you must be blind.

Chancellor: To me, she's nothing more than a monster tainted
with a blood curse.

Who did this to her!! Watch your mouth!! Such mockery will
not be tolerated any further!!
Chancellor: You've had your fun. The game ends here.

Chancellor: Now do it!! A touching reunion indeed! But the
tears will be replaced by a flood of blood!!

Princess: I won't forgive... won't forgive won't forgive
won't forgive won't forgive!!
No... I don't want this... please stop!!!!
